column3: CREATE DATABASE `inventory` CHARSET latin1 COLLATE latin1_swedish_ci

CREATE TABLE `sales` (
  `usergender` mediumtext,
  `usercity` mediumtext,
  `usersentiment` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zipcode` mediumtext,
  `sku` mediumtext,
  `createdate` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `category` mediumtext,
  `price` decimal(12,5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `county` mediumtext,
  `countycode` mediumtext,
  `userstate` mediumtext,
  `categorygroup` mediumtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`createdate`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

CREATE TABLE `products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` varchar(512) DEFAULT NULL,
  `weight` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=110 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

CREATE TABLE `nopkey` (
  `usergender` mediumtext,
  `usercity` mediumtext,
  `usersentiment` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zipcode` mediumtext,
  `sku` mediumtext,
  `createdate` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `category` mediumtext,
  `price` decimal(12,5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `county` mediumtext,
  `countycode` mediumtext,
  `userstate` mediumtext,
  `categorygroup` mediumtext
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

CREATE TABLE `debezium_signals` (
  `id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(32) NOT NULL,
  `data` varchar(2048) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1
